Directory /smart
        Top level SMART directory

Doc/            Documentation
Sample/         Samples of SMART scripts and collection.  Scripts here
                are only examples
Install/        Files need for installation.  To install smart,
                edit Install/makefile and type "make"
lib/            Auxiliary files needed by SMART.  These include the
                standard stopword list, and the standard specification
                defaults
src/            Source hierarchy
